22:05.880 --> 22:08.714
It was not her grief;
it was theirs.

22:08.760 --> 22:10.752
No longer merely
her experience,

22:10.800 --> 22:13.554
they reclaimed it
as their own.

22:13.600 --> 22:15.671
Over the course
of the following year,

22:15.720 --> 22:19.600
The song would become
an anthem for the nation.

22:19.640 --> 22:23.111
