36:28.360 --> 36:31.000
Stockholm was home
to what business scholars

36:31.040 --> 36:34.033
and economic geographers call
an industry cluster,

36:34.080 --> 36:37.118
an agglomeration of talent,
business infrastructure,

36:37.160 --> 36:39.231
