from America.

36:53.680 --> 36:58.072
To combat this threat, municipal schools
of music spread across the country,

36:58.120 --> 37:01.557
offering morally uplifting
instruction in classical music.

37:01.600 --> 37:05.116
One thing would eventually
to another.

37:05.200 --> 37:08.193
Born at the height
of this morally uplifting boom

37:08.240 --> 37:10.311
